ComicInfo.Summary:
An untalkative prisoner is put on the rack to stretch his tongue.
A soldier in the middle of a firefight would rather not smoke cigarettes because that could be harmful to his health.
Mister Big nose is invisible but only from one angle.
Atomic energy makes itself more palatable to Americans by forming a happy face in their mushroom clouds.
